parameters.name: EvaluationId
parameters.description: The ID of the evaluation task. At least one of the trace ID or task ID must be set.

parameters.name: MostRecentResultsOnly
parameters.description: The same trace data may have been evaluated by different tasks. If no task ID is specified and there are multiple evaluation results for the same trace ID, this parameter specifies whether to return only the most recent evaluation result.

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The current page number. Value range: integers greater than 0. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: TraceIds
parameters.description: Specify a set of trace IDs, and only return the evaluation results for these traces. At least one of the trace ID or task ID must be set.
